                | , 
                a(href="http://sass-lang.com/", target="_blank") SASS 
                | and 
                a(href="http://gulpjs.com/", target="_blank") Gulp.js. 
                | If you are interested,  check out the code here:

            p &#8605; 
                a(href="https://github.com/joaosaro/mysite", target="_blank") www.github.com/joaosaro/mysite

